                <h1>Understanding Natural Disasters: Causes and Impacts</h1>
                <p>Natural disasters, such as earthquakes, hurricanes, floods, and wildfires, profoundly impact communities and ecosystems. These events can cause significant loss of life and property, disrupt economies, and challenge emergency preparedness. Understanding their causes, effects, and mitigation strategies is vital for enhancing resilience and recovery efforts.</p>
